
  Wigglytuff    Normal Type Pokémon

  The body is soft and rubbery. 
   When angered, it will suck in 
  air and inflate itself to an 
  enormous size. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Igglybuff ► Jigglypuff ► Wigglytuff

